        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks ADeB for sending specimens of <hi rend="italic">Utricularia</hi> to Francis [Darwin]. Urges him to publish his observations, because <hi rend="italic">Utricularia</hi> differs widely from <hi rend="italic">Drosera</hi>. CD has been unable to detect any evidence of true digestion in <hi rend="italic">Utricularia</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
